   "text": "But anyways, here's the park. And the one big skyscraper. It's right there. It's a bank."
  },
  {
   "start": 531.86,
   "end": 540.86,
   "text": "Here you go. Jaywalkers. Pretty typical. Some more over there. Walking across the street."
  },
  {
   "start": 541.86,
   "end": 552.94,
   "text": "Here's the river of Tehranah. Some big buildings. You can see the cliffs and the mountain in the background."
  },
  {
   "start": 552.94,
   "end": 561.35,
   "text": "Here's the river. Not very big. It's actually a lot bigger today. I could have sworn than it was yesterday."
  },
  {
   "start": 562.35,
   "end": 565.35,
   "text": "But it's pretty because they have the greenery on the side."
  },
  {
   "start": 566.35,
   "end": 569.35,
   "text": "I guess it gets bigger when it's raining. That'd be cool."
  },
  {
   "start": 570.35,
   "end": 572.35,
   "text": "We got some guy. Chilling."
  },
  {
   "start": 574.6,
   "end": 579.6,
   "text": "And here's the traffic. This is like a block from my hostel. We're only a couple blocks in the center."
  },
  {
   "start": 579.6,
   "end": 585.6,
   "text": "Central part is pretty small. There's some typical Albanians walking around."
  },
  {
   "start": 586.6,
   "end": 590.6,
   "text": "Women have nice dresses here. They dress nicely."
  },
  {
   "start": 591.6,
   "end": 597.6,
   "text": "Oh, look. They've got an old army truck going down the road."
  },
  {
   "start": 598.6,
   "end": 601.6,
   "text": "And it's hot, man. I have to wash my clothes."
  },
  {
   "start": 601.6,
   "end": 603.6,
   "text": "So, congrats."
  }
 ]
}